{"tid":1060954,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[揚威國際］陳法拉將跟影后Nicole Kidman 拍HBO劇集","createTime":"2019-03-14T05:29:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T06:23:51.000Z","uid":41351,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"996b06ece376f0e7934d1fda953e1668577be51b","tid":1060954,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T05:29:04.000Z","msg":"HBO近年推出多套自家製大熱劇，包括《權力遊戲》 （Game of Thrones）、《西部世界》（Westworld）及《小謊言》（Big Little Lies）等，近日亦拍板開拍改編自Jean Hanff Korelitz小說《You Should Have Known》的全新迷你劇《The Undoing》，主角有英國男星曉格蘭特（Hugh Grant）、金像影后妮歌潔曼（Nicole Kidman）、加拿大老戲骨當奴修打蘭（Donald Sutherland），連來自香港的陳法拉亦在演員名單之上。<br />\n<br />\n《The Undoing》是一套六集的連續劇，曉格蘭特在劇中與妮歌潔曼扮演夫妻，故事講述妮歌是個生活美滿的治療師Grace Sachs，不僅有個好丈夫，入讀名校的乖仔亦令她感到安慰，可是在其首本著作推出前夕，丈夫突然失蹤，接連的衝擊令她徬徨無助。至於首拍美劇的陳法拉，於IMDb網站中資料所見，她今次飾演Jolene一角，在六集中佔有四集戲份，亦是一個重要角色。"},{"pid":"891df8f1309480c09c045145f2166b483282d98d","tid":1060954,"uid":41351,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T05:30:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RZeW2jA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRZeW2jA.png&h=7c9baa52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTvb走寶了"},{"pid":"56936d1bc243ec3e73e7ddfa969c2154c34e1106","tid":1060954,"uid":27415,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T05:30:21.000Z","msg":"法拉真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33fe0e5265ba29d652b53a73d7950c11d8f41e57","tid":1060954,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T05:30:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcae1bb78a0f08dfd7df5bc7cb412a0f960ba633","tid":1060954,"uid":198245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T05:32:14.000Z","msg":"老女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgm